                        <a class="text-dark" data-toggle="collapse" href="#q3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                            <i class="fal fa-chevron-right float-right"></i>
                            How secure is my data?
                        </a>
                    </h6>
                </div>
